Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Manager

  • public class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
    Facade class that manages the state of the application (logged in member, reservation, parking system, etc.)

      • doChangePassword

        public STATUS doChangePassword(java.lang.String oldPsw,
                               java.lang.String newPsw)
        Handle password change.
        Parameters:
        oldPsw - The old password, for verification.
        newPsw - The new password.
        Returns:
        SUCCESS if successful, PASSWORD_INVALID if new password is invalid format, FAILED if verification of old login info failed, PASSWORD_REUSE if the new password matches the old password.
        Precondition:
        Member must be logged in prior to function call.
